    "description": "<strong>The Gameplay</strong><br><u>Let's get some slimes!</u><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161120/extras/b17fa66fd5b54c46c73accf816c3b36e.poster.avif?t=1692399406\" width=602 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161120/extras/b17fa66fd5b54c46c73accf816c3b36e.webm?t=1692399406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161120/extras/b17fa66fd5b54c46c73accf816c3b36e.mp4?t=1692399406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>With a limited movement, you need to think carefully about every step until you reach the door. <br>Sometimes the door will need keys.</u><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161120/extras/60468c6b46ebbd05da8f915d525db769.poster.avif?t=1692399406\" width=602 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161120/extras/60468c6b46ebbd05da8f915d525db769.webm?t=1692399406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161120/extras/60468c6b46ebbd05da8f915d525db769.mp4?t=1692399406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>You will need to attack! Every level you have a specific quantity of daggers to use in the slimes.</u><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161120/extras/0ea80ab4870629d636d9a597bf4eca48.poster.avif?t=1692399406\" width=602 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161120/extras/0ea80ab4870629d636d9a597bf4eca48.webm?t=1692399406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161120/extras/0ea80ab4870629d636d9a597bf4eca48.mp4?t=1692399406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Be wise when you gonna strike!</u><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br>♦ 4 Worlds with unique environments<br>♦ 35 hand-craft levels<br>♦ Difficulty progression for a growing challenge over the levels<br>♦ Beautiful pixel art<br>♦ A lot of slimes to slay!",
